OL,3,CNI charity calls on Executive for paid
OL,4,Cleave for caregivers on Carers Day
OL,6,FA charity that represents carers in
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland is calling on the
OL,8,FExecutive to bring forward paid
OL,9,Fcarer's leave.
OL,11,FNew research from Carers NI has
OL,12,Frevealed that the region has the
OL,13,Fhighest proportion of unpaid carers in
OL,14,Fthe United Kingdom.
OL,16,FThursday 21 November is Carers Rights
OL,17,FDay, a milestone event for Northern
OL,18,FIreland's 220,000 carers who provide
OL,19,Fhundreds of thousands of hours of care
OL,20,Feach week whilst juggling their other
OL,21,Fresponsibilities.
