OL,6,FAine Magee from Carers NI said her
OL,7,Forganisation is marking the occasion
OL,8,Fby calling for carer's rights to be an
OL,9,FExecutive priority and highlighting
OL,10,Fthe importance of statutory paid leave
OL,11,Ffor caregivers.
OL,13,FShe said: "Unpaid carers play a
OL,14,Fcritical role in the life of the
OL,15,Fhealth service in NI and are
OL,16,Fincreasingly stepping in to fill the
OL,17,Fgaps as services worsen.
