OL,6,F"We all know NI's population is
OL,7,Fgetting older and on top of that we
OL,8,Fhave a sicker population with the
OL,9,Fnumber of people with limiting long-
OL,10,Fterm health conditions or disabilities
OL,11,Frising and impacting nearly 1 in 4
OL,12,Fresidents.
OL,14,F"We also have a major decline in the
OL,15,Fprovision of statutory care with the
OL,16,Fnumber of hours reduced by 23,000
OL,17,Fhours since 2011.
OL,19,F"So, it's no surprise that we have a
OL,20,Fmajor issue with support and rights
OL,21,Ffor carers."
