OL,6,F"What the NI government need to do is
OL,7,Ffirstly list carers as a priority
OL,8,Fwithin the forthcoming programme for
OL,9,Fgovernment and secondly, embed
OL,10,Fstronger employment and social
OL,11,Flegislative rights to help lift carers
OL,12,Fout of poverty, keep them supported in
OL,13,Femployment and help them access timely
OL,14,Fand equitable supports without having
OL,15,Fto fight for help every step of the
OL,16,Fway."
OL,18,FPeter Privilege and his wife Jean care
OL,19,Ffor her brother who is living with
OL,20,Fdementia.
