OL,6,FExplaining the impact on their lives,
OL,7,FPeter said: "Truthfully, I think at
OL,8,Fthe moment we do not have a life
OL,9,Fbecause it is taken up by my brother-
OL,10,Fin-law.
OL,12,F"You work all your life and you retire
OL,13,Fand you think you are going to do
OL,14,Fgreat things. That is gone. Your time
OL,15,Fis really not your own.
OL,17,F"It is very hard to go on a holiday or
OL,18,Fto go anywhere."
