OL,6,FOn Carers Rights Day, Peter and Jean
OL,7,Fwere enjoyed some well-deserved
OL,8,Frespite at Newington Day Centre in
OL,9,FBelfast.
OL,11,FService Manager Margaret McCrudden
OL,12,Fstressed the important role carers
OL,13,Fplay in society and the help and
OL,14,Fsupport that is available.
OL,16,F"Many people do not even recognise
OL,17,Fthat title. They'll come along and
OL,18,Fsay, 'I'm not a carer'.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
