OL,6,F"They think it's a paid position. Then
OL,7,Fyou say, 'No, but you are supporting a
OL,8,Fmother, father, brother, sister, and
OL,9,Fthey will say, but that's my duty.
OL,11,F"So many carers don't even see
OL,12,Fthemselves as a carer."
OL,14,FCarers NI have said there has been a
OL,15,Fshift in the intensity of care and the
OL,16,Fnumber of carers in Northern Ireland
OL,17,Fis rising. Help and support for carers
OL,18,Fis available on the Carers NI website
